==== 加拿大 ====
在加拿大很多城市，有眾多市民走上街頭，響應美國華盛頓的反川普大遊行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2017/01/21/trump-protests-canada_n_14304656.html|title=Canadians Take To The Streets To Support Women's Rights In Shadow Of Trump|date=January 21, 2017|4=|publisher=Huffington Post|accessdate=January 23, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170125003638/http://www.huffingtonpost.ca/2017/01/21/trump-protests-canada_n_14304656.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/thousands-of-canadians-join-women-s-marches-across-country-1.3250996|title=Thousands of Canadians join Women’s Marches across country|date=January 21, 2017|4=|publisher=CTV News|accessdate=January 23, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124072255/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/thousands-of-canadians-join-women-s-marches-across-country-1.3250996|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[多倫多|多倫多]]，上千名示威者聚集在省議會前的[[皇后公園_(多倫多)|皇后公園]]，高舉著包括「女性權利」、「我與她站在一起」等的標語牌，沿著多倫多市區一條主要大街緩慢遊行。遊行隊伍途徑美國駐多倫多大使館，並最終聚集在市政廳前的[[彌敦菲臘廣場|彌敦菲臘廣場]]。警方估計這次遊行至少有6,000人參與。

在[[渥太華|渥太華]]，有6,000至8,000名左右的示威人士，從市政廳外的人權紀念碑出發，遊行至布朗森中心，以此響應華盛頓的反川普遊行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20170122/tab1_r.htm|title=多市6000人示威反特朗普聲援華盛頓婦女大遊行|date=2017年1月21日, 2016|publisher=[[明報|明報]]|accessdate=2017年1月3日|archive-date=2017年2月2日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202075009/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20170122/tab1_r.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/ottawa/womens-march-ottawa-thousands-1.3946547|title=Moments from the March: Ottawa women cheer from hair salon, 94-year-old says 'get on with it'|date=Jan 21, 2017|publisher=CBC News|accessdate=Jan 29, 2017|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202050725/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/ottawa/womens-march-ottawa-thousands-1.3946547|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]，警方估計有高達一萬人參加了在市中心舉行的集會遊行。示威者並經過了即將落成的特朗普大廈，並在圍欄上留下示威標語，甚至有人向大廈擲雞蛋。

據統計，加拿大全國當天有超過30場遊行，包括在[[滿地可|滿地可]]、[[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]等地<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/womens-march-washington-canada-1.3942705|title=Solidarity sisters! Why Canadians are joining the Women's March on Washington|date=January 21, 2017|4=|publisher=CBC|accessdate=January 23, 2017|archive-date=2019-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327030755/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/womens-march-washington-canada-1.3942705|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2017/01/21/events-organized-in-toronto-montreal-support-washington-womens-march.html|title=‘You are part of history right now,’ Toronto women’s march told|date=January 21, 2017|4=|publisher=The Star|accessdate=January 23, 2017|archive-date=2017-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170124074946/https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/2017/01/21/events-organized-in-toronto-montreal-support-washington-womens-march.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

